{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tag-js","path":"/tag/qiang-mian-lu-hua/","webpackCompilationHash":"c05de8f8e24aa66aa83f","result":{"data":{"ghostTag":{"slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","name":"墙面绿化","visibility":"public","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null},"allGhostPost":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d3a5d90be87e20f34d374c8","title":"安友科技告诉您植物墙的后期养护怎么做！","slug":"an-you-ke-ji-gao-su-nin-zhi-wu-qiang-de-hou-qi-yang-hu-yao-zen-yao-zuo","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/6-9.jpg","excerpt":"垂直绿化是一种特殊设计的墙体，它由绿色植物构成，经过设计师的艺术处理，使其更像是装饰品。","custom_excerpt":"垂直绿化是一种特殊设计的墙体，它由绿色植物构成，经过设计师的艺术处理，使其更像是装饰品。","created_at_pretty":"26 July, 2019","published_at_pretty":"26 July, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"26 July, 2019","created_at":"2019-07-26T09:55:28.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-07-26T09:58:26.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-07-26T10:13:38.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"中国建筑绿化网","slug":"a-green","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/logo-2-1.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"中国建筑绿化网","slug":"a-green","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/logo-2-1.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"}],"plaintext":"垂直绿化是一种特殊设计的墙体，它由绿色植物构成，经过设计师的艺术处理，使其更像是装饰品。但是区别于普通装饰品，垂直绿化能分隔空间，有具备自然植物的色彩，美感十足，同时又让人感觉舒适。\n\n垂直绿化能根据不同的环境需求，设计出各种墙体造型，比如大脚怪、蝴蝶等虚实的事物。\n\n在生态上，植物墙\n具备什么样的功能，主要取决于植物的种类，有些植物擅长吸附甲醛苯，有些植物擅长吸附二氧化硫或者一氧化碳。可以因地制宜，选择合适的植物。此外，植物墙能为局部小环境降温，能增加空气湿度，清新空气。\n\n植物墙的后期养护要怎么做？\n1、浇水\n注重干湿循环，湿度太大容易有病害。\n\n2、通风\n最大限度增加垂直绿化周边的空气流动和循环。\n\n3、光照\n植物正常生长需要一定时长的光照，需要尽量满足。\n\n4、施肥\n要保证施肥的周期，根据植物墙植物的种类选择肥料。观叶选择氮肥为主，观花磷钾肥为主。还要注意，不能让植物过度生长。\n\n5、修剪\n要保证植物墙的景观效果，需要修剪过长的枝条，还可以用生长调节剂控制植物生长。\n\n一般情况下，植物墙的养护其实并不需要太多的专业知识，只需要做好以上五点即可。","html":"<p>垂直绿化是一种特殊设计的墙体，它由绿色植物构成，经过设计师的艺术处理，使其更像是装饰品。但是区别于普通装饰品，垂直绿化能分隔空间，有具备自然植物的色彩，美感十足，同时又让人感觉舒适。</p><p>垂直绿化能根据不同的环境需求，设计出各种墙体造型，比如大脚怪、蝴蝶等虚实的事物。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/1-16.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>在生态上，<u>植物墙</u>具备什么样的功能，主要取决于植物的种类，有些植物擅长吸附甲醛苯，有些植物擅长吸附二氧化硫或者一氧化碳。可以因地制宜，选择合适的植物。此外，植物墙能为局部小环境降温，能增加空气湿度，清新空气。</p><h2 id=\"-\">植物墙的后期养护要怎么做？</h2><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/2-16.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><h3 id=\"1-\">1、浇水</h3><p>注重干湿循环，湿度太大容易有病害。</p><h3 id=\"2-\">2、通风</h3><p>最大限度增加垂直绿化周边的空气流动和循环。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/3-13.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><h3 id=\"3-\">3、光照</h3><p>植物正常生长需要一定时长的光照，需要尽量满足。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/4-7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><h3 id=\"4-\">4、施肥</h3><p>要保证施肥的周期，根据<u>植物墙植物</u>的种类选择肥料。观叶选择氮肥为主，观花磷钾肥为主。还要注意，不能让植物过度生长。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/5-3.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><h3 id=\"5-\">5、修剪</h3><p>要保证植物墙的景观效果，需要修剪过长的枝条，还可以用生长调节剂控制植物生长。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/6-8.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>一般情况下，植物墙的养护其实并不需要太多的专业知识，只需要做好以上五点即可。</p>","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/an-you-ke-ji-gao-su-nin-zhi-wu-qiang-de-hou-qi-yang-hu-yao-zen-yao-zuo/","uuid":"d26094dd-5acd-478d-a685-7ce787c1ed67","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d3a5d90be87e20f34d374c8"}},{"node":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d365e2dbe87e20f34d3740f","title":"迪拜用绿植墙壁做景，为居民提供诗意般的生活！","slug":"di-bai-yong-lu-zhi-qiang-bi-zuo-jing-wei-ju-min-ti-gong-shi-yi-ban-de-sheng-huo","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/22-1.jpg","excerpt":"这面墙位于文化村的中心，能俯瞰历史悠久的迪拜河。","custom_excerpt":"这面墙位于文化村的中心，能俯瞰历史悠久的迪拜河。","created_at_pretty":"23 July, 2019","published_at_pretty":"23 July, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"15 August, 2019","created_at":"2019-07-23T09:09:01.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-07-23T09:13:11.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-08-15T09:46:45.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"中国建筑绿化网","slug":"a-green","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/logo-2-1.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"中国建筑绿化网","slug":"a-green","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/logo-2-1.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"}],"plaintext":"2018年9月1号全球最大的绿色墙壁，在中东的迪拜码头完工。这面墙位于文化村的中心，能俯瞰历史悠久的迪拜河。\n\n绿色墙壁长210米，高6米，共有1260㎡。整面墙有80000株绿植，每年可抵消约4.4万吨的二氧化碳。\n\n城市热量，主要是沥青和建筑材料吸收太阳热量后导致的。绿色墙壁可通过光合作用抵消建筑排出的热量。在夏季公园内漫步，你能明显地感觉到这种效果。据科学测试，绿植墙壁能将周围温度降低5℃左右。\n\n迪拜物业集团的首席执行官Raed AI\nNuaimi在记者采访时说：“根据2018年世界幸福报告，阿联酋是世界上最幸福的20个国家之一”这表明我们对可持续生活环境的热心支持。我们致力于提高生活质量和幸福度。\n\n\n2007年之后，迪拜市区的93％都安装了绿色墙壁。因为它们发现，绿色墙壁有助于降低建筑物的整体温度。迪拜许多著名的公共场所都可见到绿色墙壁的身影，如机场与购物中心。\n\n\n迪拜意识到绿植墙壁不仅是可持续发展的元素，而且绿色的生活方式能让居民更加高兴。迪拜码头的绿植墙壁就是一个典型的案例。它为整个社区带来了一种宁静，优化了当地的生态系统。","html":"<p>2018年9月1号全球最大的绿色墙壁，在中东的迪拜码头完工。这面墙位于文化村的中心，能俯瞰历史悠久的迪拜河。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/1-3.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>绿色墙壁长210米，高6米，共有1260㎡。整面墙有80000株绿植，每年可抵消约4.4万吨的二氧化碳。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/22.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>城市热量，主要是沥青和建筑材料吸收太阳热量后导致的。绿色墙壁可通过光合作用抵消建筑排出的热量。在夏季公园内漫步，你能明显地感觉到这种效果。据科学测试，绿植墙壁能将周围温度降低5℃左右。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/44.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>迪拜物业集团的首席执行官Raed AI Nuaimi在记者采访时说：“根据2018年世界幸福报告，阿联酋是世界上最幸福的20个国家之一”这表明我们对可持续生活环境的热心支持。我们致力于提高生活质量和幸福度。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/55.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p><br>2007年之后，迪拜市区的93％都安装了绿色墙壁。因为它们发现，绿色墙壁有助于降低建筑物的整体温度。迪拜许多著名的公共场所都可见到绿色墙壁的身影，如机场与购物中心。<br></p><p>迪拜意识到绿植墙壁不仅是可持续发展的元素，而且绿色的生活方式能让居民更加高兴。迪拜码头的绿植墙壁就是一个典型的案例。它为整个社区带来了一种宁静，优化了当地的生态系统。</p>","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/di-bai-yong-lu-zhi-qiang-bi-zuo-jing-wei-ju-min-ti-gong-shi-yi-ban-de-sheng-huo/","uuid":"a2f7a25a-0e64-40ec-a173-2e110e98444d","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d365e2dbe87e20f34d3740f"}},{"node":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11d3f895f47f36568541fc","title":"植物墙造景，让你的店铺更具特色！","slug":"zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/9-1-1.jpg","excerpt":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。","custom_excerpt":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"26 June, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T15:57:44.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T16:00:42.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-06-26T09:27:40.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"}],"primary_author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"},"primary_tag":{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"#室内墙面绿化","slug":"hash-shi-nei-qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":null,"feature_image":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520157646479-22f25713523d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1080&fit=max&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjExNzczfQ","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"internal"}],"plaintext":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。而消费的减少会直接影响其盈利水平，这使的很多商店在经营上越发困难！\n\n国外很多商店为避免这种情况，会在室内打造生机勃勃的植物墙。这种室内造景的方式，可增加室内景观让客户有更加愉悦的购物体验。同时在与对手竞争时，植物墙能帮助品牌在客户的心理上建立印象认知。\n\n营业不佳有多方面因素，但富有特色的装修是吸引客户到店消费的一大利器。很多商店其环境一般、装修一般、视觉设计一般、整体给人感觉死气沉沉，这更别说让人前来消费。好的设计是通向成功的第一步！\n\n植物墙能增加室内生机，使购物过程不在枯燥无味。并且植物墙能够传达其健康的品牌理念，向客户表明其产品健康的自然性、无污染、无化学性。\n\n目前，越来越多的商家开始在自家的店铺内增加绿植。绿植能使整个店铺更具郁郁葱葱的生机和文化特色。在一些美食店，用植物墙做装饰点缀，不仅能体现其食材的自然性，也能展示其就餐环境的干净性。","html":"<p>对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。而消费的减少会直接影响其盈利水平，这使的很多商店在经营上越发困难！</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/1-4.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2-2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>国外很多商店为避免这种情况，会在室内打造生机勃勃的植物墙。这种室内造景的方式，可增加室内景观让客户有更加愉悦的购物体验。同时在与对手竞争时，植物墙能帮助品牌在客户的心理上建立印象认知。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/3-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/4-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>营业不佳有多方面因素，但富有特色的装修是吸引客户到店消费的一大利器。很多商店其环境一般、装修一般、视觉设计一般、整体给人感觉死气沉沉，这更别说让人前来消费。好的设计是通向成功的第一步！</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/5-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/6-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>植物墙能增加室内生机，使购物过程不在枯燥无味。并且植物墙能够传达其健康的品牌理念，向客户表明其产品健康的自然性、无污染、无化学性。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/8.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>目前，越来越多的商家开始在自家的店铺内增加绿植。绿植能使整个店铺更具郁郁葱葱的生机和文化特色。在一些美食店，用植物墙做装饰点缀，不仅能体现其食材的自然性，也能展示其就餐环境的干净性。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/9-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image-->","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se/","uuid":"90f16ea3-7681-45f5-8267-1ab11fa0273c","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d11d3f895f47f36568541fc"}},{"node":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11c5f995f47f365685419b","title":"爱照顾绿植，就弄个垂直植物墙吧！","slug":"ai-zhao-gu-lu-zhi-jiu-nong-ge-chui-zhi-zhi-wu-qiang-ba","featured":true,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/4.jpg","excerpt":"我一个朋友所在的公司进行一整层写字楼的全面装修她想把会议室的一面墙壁上栽上满满的植物","custom_excerpt":"我一个朋友所在的公司进行一整层写字楼的全面装修她想把会议室的一面墙壁上栽上满满的植物","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"27 June, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T14:58:01.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T15:01:49.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-06-27T15:21:58.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[